messages.text: Hey
Where are you? I’m here at the East Gate.
I’m not associating with liars anymore
It’s gotten me into too much trouble.
What do you mean?
You could have told me I was part of some gross experiment
My friend Sasha found your papers. The web.
I can explain
All liars can fucking explain
Explaining’s what liars do best
Spinning more lies
I’m ruined now, because of your lies. I’m a freak.
I’ll probably be killed by the FBI. They’ve already kidnapped Sasha.
What???
WHY is the question. Why do I have this…disease?
Why did you infect those other girls?
It came from a good place, I promise.
it was a test. A successful test.
Successful in securing me a career in a travelling circus?
Because I don’t know what the fuck you’re talking about right now
Because we had unprotected sex, you are now immune to herpes.
Oh shut up.
It’s true! Dr. Hyland discovered it.
Remember her lecture on folk medicine that Prof.
Stafford made us go to last semester?
Yes. Snooze-fest.
Reptiles are used in all kinds of traditional medicine, as we learned
those shamans and witch doctors knew their shit
I mean, we shouldn’t have been surprised.
More and more of these discoveries are being made daily.
I personally believe that it’s our responsibility as scientists and doctors...
to focus on ridding ourselves of the colonialist impulse to frown on non-Western medicine
Spare me the anthropology lesson. Just explain.
Sorry. Dr. Hyland has been experimenting on rats for a decade...
and found that splicing their genes with those of certain reptiles and amphibians actually eliminated herpes in the rats -
and that their offspring were born herpes-free
THEN she found out that the males who mated with the females not only transmitted the “vaccine” to their offspring...
but to their partners
this vaccine was not only genetically transmitted, it was sexually transmitted
so then she tried it out with humans?
Exactly
Ok, and she didn’t publish any of the rat findings—why?
She DID. 3 years ago
no one paid attention. Blame the patriarchal science world.
Blame the patriarchy?
This is coming from the dude who INTENTIONALLY infected women with an untested “vaccine” WITHOUT THEIR CONSENT?
You, my friend, are a glowing beacon of feminism.
Ugh. Do you understand what I’m saying? YOU’RE NEVER GOING TO GET HERPES.
How do you know?
100% of rats were cured, and 100% were born herpes-free.
Ok, so maybe there’s a chance I won’t get herpes.
But I’ll have to live with these mutations.
I would rather have herpes, now that I think of it.
The side effects are an…issue.
But once you get used to them, they aren’t all bad
Some of us have found them to be advantageous
Actually, that’s what I wanted to tell you
I’m getting to a point where my hands…
it’s getting harder and harder to text, to talk, to see like a human
I think I’m going to disappear for a while
will you come with me?
There are a group of us living out here
Why would I come with you?
after you used me like one of Dr. Hyland’s lab rats
You know, I was going to tell you about all this over coffee
But you stood me up
Are you seriously dredging that up again?
I don’t want to fight, ok?
I stupidly thought that you hooked up with me because you enjoyed our conversation
Hey now
I did enjoy our conversation
I’ve had a crush on you since freshman orientation
really?
YES. You just never paid any attention to me.
Then we were at that party together and I knew I had to make a move
And if I’d known this is how it would turn out, then I wouldn’t have done it
How can I prove to you how sorry I am
I don’t need you to PROVE anything
I think I just need time to process all of this
Hey, does your friend Sasha have short pink hair?
Yes. She did that for the sole purpose of pissing off her mom. Why??
I think I see her
where??
She’s in a chair.
There’s a van. And some agent-y looking guys
Ugh. Some FBI creep texted me from her phone. We’re supposed to meet at 2
We were fighting, S and I. I never wanted anything like this to happen, though
Hold on, let me get closer
Where are you?
Do you know the lookout point overlooking Lake Finch?
That’s where they are.
I’m running over now
don’t let them see you
I’m getting closer…
They’ve got her tied up. It looks like they’re interrogating her…
Hang on
Tell me what you see
Anders??
Hello?
WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT
Please tell me those were fireworks
ANDERS PLEASE TEXT ME BACK
